snippet.title: I had too much fun making this shitpost of a game
snippet.description:
This game is called "6ftBlunder", it is free to download in itch.io. It is a game that I had a lot of fun making, and seeing how it inevitably turned out. This is the game amongst my catalogue that I would most easily recommend to my friends, because it is silly, encapsulates my humor, and easy.

The twist at the end of the true ending also goes pretty hard.

Download:
https://kiyopawn.itch.io/6-ft-blunder

If this video interested you in my works, feel free to check out my other works in itch.io, or check out this channel to see the development of my passion project.

Itch.io Page
https://kiyopawn.itch.io/
